00253 {
00254         std::wstring names[] = {L"prefix-one", L"two", L"prefix-three"};
00255         ParameterNameValueType t;
00256

00263         
00264         ParameterNameValueTypeVector v;
00265         header->GetNameValParamsBeginsWith(L"prefix-", v);
00266         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(v.size() == 2);
00267         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(v.at(0).GetName() == names[0]);
00268         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(v.at(1).GetName() == names[2]);
